channel.title: [SHOWOFF]New Armadyl and Dragon Armor! :D [SHOWOFF]
channel.description:
Alright, as you all know, I've just release a V2 server, but i was thinking, and i need to upgrade from old, regular PI's. So i thought "Why not make new armor models." So, I made these and also made them for PI!
[IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/PleaseVote.gif[/img]
[b]Please Give Full Constructive Chritisizim! Thanks![/b]
Armadyl Full Helm [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/armahelm.jpg[/img]
Armadyl Platebody [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/armabody.jpg[/img]
Armadyl Platelegs [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/armalegs-1.jpg[/img]
Full Armadyl [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/newarmadylarmorfull.jpg[/img]
Ok. Now for dragon.
Dragon Full Helm (or) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/dragonhelm.jpg[/img]
Dragon Platebody (or) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/dragonbody.jpg[/img]
Dragon Platelegs (or) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/dragonlegs.jpg[/img]
Dragon Boots (or) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/dragonboots.jpg[/img]
Dragon Full Set (or) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/newdragonarmorfull.jpg[/img]
I put about a week worth of work into these. I MIGHT release if I have good comments. But PLEASE be truthful.! Thanks!
